---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Liquid Desiccant Climate Control | PCT Patented | 14 Years Field Proven | Enerama"
  description="The Climate Control System That Pays for Itself. 30–70% less energy. Water extracted from air. Proven in 27 real-world projects across 3 countries."
  keywords="liquid desiccant, dragon platform, PCT patent, dehumidification, water from air, solar thermal HVAC, industrial climate control, dragon solar TES"
  canonicalPath="/technology"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-20" style="background-color: #0B3D4C;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-medium" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          PCT Patented · 14 Years Field Proven
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 text-balance">
          The Climate Control System That Pays for Itself
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          30–70% less energy. Water extracted from air. Proven in 27 real-world projects across 3 countries — 14 Years field-proven.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
            style="background-color: #E07B39;"
          >
            Download Technical Brief
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-lg border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#0B3D4C] transition-colors"
          >
            Book a Technical Demo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero Stats -->
  <section class="py-12 border-b" style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">350+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Installed Conditioners</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">2,830 kW</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Installed Power</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">11,792 L/h</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Installed Water Extraction</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">14 Years</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Continuous Operation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Capturing & Reusing Latent Energy -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Capturing & Reusing Latent Energy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          PCT Patented Liquid Desiccant Technology — 14 Years Field Proven
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Market Forces -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          The Market Has Never Needed This More
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Four forces are converging — right now
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-4" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">$240B → $370B</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">Global HVAC Market by 2030</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Fastest-growing segment: energy-efficient systems</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-4" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">+40%</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">Energy Costs Since 2021</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Industrial operators under intense pressure to cut consumption</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-4" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">2B+</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">People Affected by Water Scarcity</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Enerama systems generate water as a byproduct of operation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-4" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">2030</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">EU & US Refrigerant Phase-Out Deadline</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Regulations forcing transition away from traditional HVAC refrigerants</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Enerama's Liquid Desiccant system addresses all four challenges simultaneously — with 14 Years of field-proven results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Our Technology Different -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
            What Makes Our Technology Different?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional climate control systems rely on refrigeration-based dehumidification, which is energy-intensive and limited in capability. Our patented Liquid Desiccant system represents a fundamental shift in how environmental control works.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            By using a hygroscopic Liquid Desiccant independently — without mechanical refrigeration, we achieve superior moisture removal, dramatically lower energy consumption, and the unique ability to extract usable water from the air.
          </p>
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-white font-semibold" style="background-color: #0D7377;">
            30–70% Energy Savings vs. Traditional Systems
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69c9538c5e6a6b66c71a24ee/69d1177b013256053a0448c7_IMG-20201202-WA0000.jpg"
            alt="Dragon Liquid Desiccant unit - close-up view"
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About the Name -->
  <section class="py-16" style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-medium text-white" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          ABOUT THE NAME
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl text-white leading-relaxed">
          <span class="font-bold">Dragon™</span> is Enerama's proprietary climate control platform — developed, field-tested, and continuously refined over 14 Years. When you see Dragon Liquid Desiccant or Dragon Solar TES, these are technologies built on and delivered through Enerama's full EPC project framework.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technology Benefits -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Technology Benefits
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Why industry leaders choose our PCT patented system
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Superior Energy Efficiency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">30–70% reduction in energy consumption compared to traditional refrigeration-based systems, delivering rapid ROI in 2–4 years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Exceptional Dehumidification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Extract over 100 liters per hour of moisture from air, maintaining precise humidity control even in challenging environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Water Generation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Unique capability to extract and purify water from ambient air, providing an additional resource for operations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Proven Reliability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Fewer moving parts and robust design mean lower maintenance requirements and extended operational life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Environmental Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Reduced carbon footprint through lower energy use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Precise Control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Independent control of temperature and humidity for optimal environmental conditions in any application.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 border-l-4" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #0D7377;">Natural Pathogen Elimination</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Airborne bacteria, mold spores, and viruses are naturally destroyed on contact with concentrated Liquid Desiccant solution — no UV lamps, no chemicals, no consumables. Critical for food processing, agriculture, and pharmaceutical environments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dragon Solar TES -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background-color: #0B3D4C;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Building on the Dragon platform's 14 Years proven reliability, Enerama is developing the next evolution in fully renewable climate control:
        </p>
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-medium text-white" style="background-color: rgba(224,123,57,0.25);">
          Next Generation Module — Pre-Commercial · PCT Patent Filed Q1 2026
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white/5 backdrop-blur p-8 md:p-12 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">
          Dragon Solar TES — Next Generation Module (Pre-Commercial)
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6" style="color: #E07B39;">
          PCT Patent Filed Q1 2026 — First field deployment in development
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Dragon Solar TES tank to store daytime solar energy and release it at night — enabling Dragon to operate on renewable energy around the clock.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          The patented innovation: solar collector output (55–80°C), Dragon regeneration band (60–75°C) overlap perfectly — no intermediate heat exchanger required.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="font-semibold text-white">Daytime:</span> solar energy stored in tank.
          <span class="font-semibold text-white ml-2">Night and cloudy periods:</span> stored heat released for uninterrupted Dragon regeneration.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
          Dragon Solar TES is currently in pre-commercial development phase. PCT patent filed Q1 2026. First field deployment planned. Built on the validated Dragon Liquid Desiccant platform with 14 Years of operational history across 27 projects.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How Liquid Desiccant Technology Works -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          How Liquid Desiccant Technology Works
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Understanding the science behind superior performance
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white" style="background-color: #0D7377;">1</div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Absorption Phase</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Ambient air passes through a Liquid Desiccant. The hygroscopic properties of Liquid Desiccant cause it to absorb moisture from the air with exceptional efficiency, simultaneously cooling the air through the absorption process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 with image -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white" style="background-color: #0D7377;">2</div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Regeneration Cycle</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The moisture-saturated Liquid Desiccant solution is heated to release the absorbed water. This regeneration process can utilize waste heat, solar thermal energy, or other low-grade heat sources, further improving overall system efficiency.
            </p>
            <img
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69c9538c5e6a6b66c71a24ee/69d1177d567f647cc6725cd6_IMG_20190503_094135.jpg"
              alt="Dragon system technical piping and unit connections"
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md mt-2"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 with image -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white" style="background-color: #0D7377;">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Water Recovery</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              During regeneration, the released moisture is condensed and collected as pure water — over 100 liters per hour. This water can be used for irrigation, cooling towers, or other operational needs.
            </p>
            <img
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69c9538c5e6a6b66c71a24ee/69d1177ba853f5d8609fdb56_Albion%205.jpg"
              alt="Dragon system metallic duct and ventilation system"
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md mt-2"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white" style="background-color: #0D7377;">4</div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Continuous Operation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              The regenerated Liquid Desiccant solution returns to the absorption phase, creating a continuous cycle. Advanced controls optimize the process based on ambient conditions and facility requirements, ensuring maximum efficiency 24/7.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- See Dragon in Action — heading + YouTube video block BELOW heading -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          See Dragon in Action
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full">
      <a
        href="https://youtu.be/0FEcOP-OiiA"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="See Dragon in Action — opens YouTube video"
        class="relative block group overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/0FEcOP-OiiA/maxresdefault.jpg"
          alt="See Dragon in Action — Liquid Desiccant system in industrial deployment"
          class="w-full h-96 object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
          onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://img.youtube.com/vi/0FEcOP-OiiA/hqdefault.jpg';"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 group-hover:bg-black/40 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center text-white">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 ml-1" fill="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-90 mt-1">Watch on YouTube</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Advantages Table -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Technical Advantages
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Why Liquid Desiccant outperforms traditional systems
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
          <thead style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-white font-semibold">Performance Metric</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-white font-semibold">Traditional Refrigeration</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-white font-semibold">Enerama Liquid Desiccant System</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Energy Consumption</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">High (baseline)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">30–70% lower</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Dehumidification Capacity</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Limited</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">100+ L/h</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Temp / Humidity Control</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Coupled (dependent)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Independent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Water Recovery</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">None</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Up to 80% recovery</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Maintenance Level</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">High (many moving parts)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Minimal</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Operating Life</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Standard</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">14 Years · Field-proven</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        * Field data: 27 commissioned projects · USA, Switzerland, Turkey · 26°C / 55% RH · 32,000 m³/h airflow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proven Across 3 Continents -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Proven Across 3 Continents
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          27 commissioned projects — real facilities, real results
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">Agriculture</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Greenhouse Climate Control</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Antalya, Turkey</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">40% energy reduction vs. prior HVAC system</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">Food Processing</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Persimmon Drying Facility</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Adana, Turkey</p>
